  53,35,"aend hdha aldhy qate eta'h eilm alghayb 'anah synfad ma fi yadah hataa 'amsik merwfh, fahu yaraa dhlk eianana? lays al'amr kdhlk, wa'iinama 'amsik ean alsdqt walmerwf walbr walslt; bkhla wshuhhana"
